msgid "Useful Note"
msgstr ""

# db0a2531855e48bbb92c176e1f7d4b62
#: ../../admin-guide/plugins/esi.en.rst:134
msgid ""
"You can provide proper cache control header and the ESI response and ESI "
"include response can be cached separately. It is extremely useful for "
"rendering page with multiple modules. The page layout can be a ESI "
"response with multiple ESI include include, each for different module. "
"The page layour ESI response can be cached and each individual ESI "
"include can also be cached with different duration."
msgstr ""

